EN: Her innermost desire is to have a happy family.

ZH: 他的欲望驱使他不停地努力工作。
EN: His desires drive him to work relentlessly.

ZH: 这个国家的人民有获得自由的欲望。
EN: The people of this country have a desire for freedom.

ZH: 我的欲望之一是世界各地旅行。
EN: One of my desires is to travel around the world.

ZH: 在生活中，我们都有自己的欲望和追求。
EN: In life, we all have our own desires and pursuits.

ZH: 他的贪婪欲望毁了他的事业和家庭。
EN: His greedy desires ruined his career and family.

ZH: 减少物品的欲望可以帮助我们过上简单的生活。
EN: Reducing the desire for possessions can help us live a simple life.

ZH: 她对时尚的欲望使她经常购物。
EN: Her desire for fashion leads her to shop often.

ZH: 欲望是人类社会不可或缺的一部分。
EN: Desire is an essential part of human society.

ZH: 过度的欲望可能带来不必要的压力和困扰。
EN: Excessive desires can bring unnecessary stress and trouble.

ZH: 能控制欲望是一种重要的心理技能。
EN: Being able to control desires is an important psychological skill.

ZH: 他常常被物质欲望所驱使，无法获得真正的满足感。
EN: He is often driven by material desires and unable to find true fulfillment.

ZH: 这个社会教会我们如何管理和满足欲望。
EN: This society teaches us how to manage and fulfill desires.

